  "reasons": [
    "The article provides largely accurate troubleshooting steps for common CircleCI 404 errors, covering project slugs, pipeline IDs, and VCS authorization issues. Claims are generally well-supported by official documentation and support resources. However, the instruction to check AWS CloudWatch logs for job details is misleading for typical CircleCI Cloud users, as native CircleCI job logs are the primary source. The description of personal API token scopes could also be more precise, as personal tokens usually grant full read/write access rather than specific, granular scopes."
